  "Description": {
    "English": "An automatic translation device. Device must be calibrated by pre-loading with existing translation data. Device must have <span class=\"name name-stellar\">network connection to Artemis</span> to function.<br><br>Without access to host translation service, on-board circuit allows limited real-time translation of a small number of words.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种自动翻译装置。设备必须通过预加载现有翻译数据进行校准，且必须<span class=\"name name-stellar\">连接到阿耳特弥斯网络</span>方能运行。<br><br>无法获取主机翻译服务时，板载电路能完成少量单词的有限实时翻译。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "自動翻譯裝置。本裝置必須事先調校，讀取現有翻譯資料。本裝置必須<span class=\"name name-stellar\">與阿耳忒彌斯保持網路連線</span>，才能正常使用。<br><br>若無法連線翻譯服務主機，裝置的內建電路，可以進行有限即時翻譯，但僅能翻譯少數單字。"
  },
